' data-slide-id="13247956"  data-component='slide'><div class="image"><img class="slide-media media-gallery-slide-media" data-src="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/62/42/27/13247956/9/gallery_medium.jpg" data-src-2x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/62/42/27/13247956/9/gallery_large.jpg" data-src-4x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/62/42/27/13247956/9/gallery_xlarge.jpg"  data-alt-title="" data-resale-link="0" alt="Vesuvio Cafe opened in 1948 and today is jointly owned by the Clyde and Fein families." /></div><figcaption  style="opacity: 0;"><span class="count">3<span>of</span>10</span><span class="caption">Vesuvio Cafe opened in 1948 and today is jointly owned by the Clyde and Fein families.</span><span class="credits">Photo: Michael Macor / The Chronicle 2017</span></figcaption></figure><figure class="gallery__slider-item" style="z-index: 3;" id="4-image-15480080" data-slide-number='4' data-slide-id="15480080"  data-component='slide'><div class="image"><img class="slide-media media-gallery-slide-media" data-src="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480080/11/gallery_medium.jpg" data-src-2x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480080/11/gallery_large.jpg" data-src-4x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480080/11/gallery_xlarge.jpg"  data-alt-title="" data-resale-link="0" alt="Alaskan king crab is among the eclectic items on the walls at Specs’, where musician Taj Mahal hung out." /></div><figcaption  style="opacity: 0;"><span class="count">4<span>of</span>10</span><span class="caption">Alaskan king crab is among the eclectic items on the walls at Specs’, where musician Taj Mahal hung out.</span><span class="credits">Photo: Mason Trinca / Special to The Chronicle 2018</span></figcaption></figure><figure class="gallery__slider-item" style="z-index: 4;" id="5-image-15480072" data-slide-number='5' data-slide-id="15480072"  data-component='slide'><div class="image"><img class="slide-media media-gallery-slide-media" data-src="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480072/9/gallery_medium.jpg" data-src-2x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480072/9/gallery_large.jpg" data-src-4x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480072/9/gallery_xlarge.jpg"  data-alt-title="" data-resale-link="0" alt="Patrons celebrate the 50th anniversary of Specs’ bar in 2018. The bar would have held a 52nd anniversary party this April 26 if it weren’t for shelter-in-place orders." /></div><figcaption  style="opacity: 0;"><span class="count">5<span>of</span>10</span><span class="caption">Patrons celebrate the 50th anniversary of Specs’ bar in 2018. The bar would have held a 52nd anniversary party this April 26 if it weren’t for shelter-in-place orders.</span><span class="credits">Photo: Mason Trinca / Special to The Chronicle 2018</span></figcaption></figure><figure class="gallery__slider-item" style="z-index: 5;" id="6-image-15480084" data-slide-number='6' data-slide-id="15480084"  data-component='slide'><div class="image"><img class="slide-media media-gallery-slide-media" data-src="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480084/9/gallery_medium.jpg" data-src-2x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480084/9/gallery_large.jpg" data-src-4x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480084/9/gallery_xlarge.jpg"  data-alt-title="" data-resale-link="0" alt="Celebrations at Specs’ frequently featured oysters, which Specs himself loved." /></div><figcaption  style="opacity: 0;"><span class="count">6<span>of</span>10</span><span class="caption">Celebrations at Specs’ frequently featured oysters, which Specs himself loved.</span><span class="credits">Photo: Mason Trinca / Special to The Chronicle 2018</span></figcaption></figure><figure class="gallery__slider-item" style="z-index: 6;" id="7-image-15480082" data-slide-number='7' data-slide-id="15480082"  data-component='slide'><div class="image"><img class="slide-media media-gallery-slide-media" data-src="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480082/11/gallery_medium.jpg" data-src-2x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480082/11/gallery_large.jpg" data-src-4x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/73/03/24/15480082/11/gallery_xlarge.jpg"  data-alt-title="" data-resale-link="0" alt="Specs’ Twelve Adler Museum Cafe is so named because of the memorabilia lining its walls." /></div><figcaption  style="opacity: 0;"><span class="count">7<span>of</span>10</span><span class="caption">Specs’ Twelve Adler Museum Cafe is so named because of the memorabilia lining its walls.</span><span class="credits">Photo: Mason Trinca / Special to The Chronicle 2018</span></figcaption></figure><figure class="gallery__slider-item" style="z-index: 7;" id="8-image-10807979" data-slide-number='8' data-slide-id="10807979"  data-component='slide'><div class="image"><img class="slide-media media-gallery-slide-media" data-src="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/51/16/52/10807979/11/gallery_medium.jpg" data-src-2x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/51/16/52/10807979/11/gallery_large.jpg" data-src-4x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/51/16/52/10807979/11/gallery_xlarge.jpg"  data-alt-title="" data-resale-link="0" alt="These busts, part of the eclectic collection at Specs’ Twelve Adler Museum Cafe, include a bust of Specs himself (right)." /></div><figcaption  style="opacity: 0;"><span class="count">8<span>of</span>10</span><span class="caption">These busts, part of the eclectic collection at Specs’ Twelve Adler Museum Cafe, include a bust of Specs himself (right).</span><span class="credits">Photo: John Storey / Special to The Chronicle 2016</span></figcaption></figure><figure class="gallery__slider-item" style="z-index: 8;" id="9-image-11437082" data-slide-number='9' data-slide-id="11437082"  data-component='slide'><div class="image"><img class="slide-media media-gallery-slide-media" data-src="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/53/50/20/11437082/7/gallery_medium.jpg" data-src-2x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/53/50/20/11437082/7/gallery_large.jpg" data-src-4x="https://s.hdnux.com/photos/53/50/20/11437082/7/gallery_xlarge.jpg"  data-alt-title="" data-resale-link="